# Construct the service object for interacting with the Compute API -
# the 'clouddebugger' service, at version 'v2'.
# You can browse other available api services and versions here:
#     https://developers.google.com/api-client-library/python/apis/
service = discovery.build('clouddebugger', 'v2', credentials=credentials)

register_debuggee_request = {}  # construct your object here
request = service.controller().debuggees().register(body=register_debuggee_request)
request.execute()
